#: ../../../virt/kvm/arm/pkvm.rst:83
msgid "Proxying of Trustzone services"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../virt/kvm/arm/pkvm.rst:85
msgid ""
"Status: FF-A and PSCI calls from the host are proxied by the pKVM hypervisor."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../virt/kvm/arm/pkvm.rst:88
msgid ""
"The FF-A proxy ensures that the host cannot share pVM or hypervisor memory "
"with Trustzone as part of a \"confused deputy\" attack."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../virt/kvm/arm/pkvm.rst:91
msgid ""
"The PSCI proxy ensures that CPUs always have the stage-2 identity map "
"installed when they are executing in the host."
msgstr ""

